            "question": "FURTHER READING: What are some books to dive into this content further?",
            "answer": "<ul><li><a href=\"https://www.christianbook.com/mere-christianity-c-s-lewis/9780060652920/pd/2926X\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.christianbook.com/mere-christianity-c-s-lewis/9780060652920/pd/2926X\"><em>Mere Christianity</em></a><em> </em>by C. S. Lewis</li><li><a href=\"https://www.jenwilkin.net/books-and-studies\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.jenwilkin.net/books-and-studies\"><em>Women of the Word</em></a><em> </em>by Jen Wilken</li><li><a href=\"https://www.nancyguthrie.com/even-better-than-eden\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.nancyguthrie.com/even-better-than-eden\"><em>Even Better than Eden</em></a><em> </em>by Nancy Guthrie</li><li><a href=\"/pages/start-from-here\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Start From Here\"><em>Start From Here</em></a><em> </em>by Ness Cannon</li><li><a href=\"https://www.lifeway.com/en/product-family/seamless\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.lifeway.com/en/product-family/seamless\"><em>Seamless</em></a><em> </em>by Angie Smith</li></ul>",
