            "question": "PODCASTS: What are some podcasts to learn in depth about the Bible?",
            "answer": "<ul><li><a href=\"https://www.journeywomen.org/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.journeywomen.org/\"><em>Journeywomen</em></a><em> </em>by Hunter Beless</li><li><a href=\"https://www.thebiblerecap.com/about\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.thebiblerecap.com/about\"><em>The Bible Recap</em></a><em> </em>by Tara-Leigh Cobble</li><li><a href=\"https://www.nancyguthrie.com/help-me-teach-the-bible-podcast\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.nancyguthrie.com/help-me-teach-the-bible-podcast\"><em>Help Me Teach the Bible</em></a><em> </em>by Nancy Guthrie</li><li><a href=\"https://www.trainingthechurch.com/knowingfaith\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.trainingthechurch.com/knowingfaith\"><em>Knowing Faith</em></a><em> </em>by Jen Wilkin, J. T. English,<br/>and Kyle Worley</li></ul>",
